ure id="attachment_3374691" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3374691" style="width: 1920px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3374691" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/The-Last-Of-Us-multiplayer-concept-art.jpg" alt="我们最后的多人游戏。图片来源：顽皮的狗。" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/The-Last-Of-Us-multiplayer-concept-art.jpg 1920w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/The-Last-Of-Us-multiplayer-concept-art-400x225.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/The-Last-Of-Us-multiplayer-concept-art-800x450.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/The-Last-Of-Us-multiplayer-concept-art-696x392.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/The-Last-Of-Us-multiplayer-concept-art-1392x783.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/The-Last-Of-Us-multiplayer-concept-art-1068x601.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3374691" class="wp-caption-text">我们最后的多人游戏。图片来源：顽皮的狗。</figcaption></figure><p>顽皮的狗<a href="https://www.naughtydog.com/blog/an_update_on_the_last_of_us_online" target="_blank" rel="noopener">宣布</a>取消，“为了<em>在网上发布和支持我们的最后一位，</em>我们必须将所有工作室资源放在支持后的启动内容后面，从而严重影响未来的单人游戏的发展。因此，我们在我们面前有两条途径：成为唯一的现场服务游戏工作室，或者继续专注于定义了顽皮狗遗产的单人叙事游戏。”</p><p>除了参与<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/the-last-of-us"><em>我们最后一个人</em></a>的HBO改编外，Naughty Dog目前正在开发播种行动 - 冒险游戏中的游戏<em>间阶级：异端先知</em>，其将以<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nine-inch-nails">9英寸指甲的</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/trent-reznor">Trent Reznor</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/atticus-ross">Atticus Ross</a>组成的分数。该工作室还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/naughty-dog-teases-one-more-chapter-with-the-last-of-us-part-3-3582616">取笑了<em>我们最后</em>一场比赛的三分之一</a>。 “另一章，”工作室负责人尼尔·德鲁克曼（Neil Druckmann）去年说。</p><p>在其他新闻中，已经确认， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-last-of-us-heres-when-season-two-is-coming-out-3839629"><em>第二</em>季第二季的第一集将于4月13日首映。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-last-of-us-multiplayer-game-cancelled-live-service-3839778">这就是为什么“伟大”“我们最后的“我们最后的多人游戏”被取消的</a>原因首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
